Add @lightly aged rum{2%oz}, @fresh lime juice{3/4%oz}, and @SC Demerara Syrup{1/2%oz} to a #cocktail shaker{}.

Add cracked or cubed ice, shake, and then double-strain into a chilled #coupe{}.
